summary: Can i ask what would Iida and shinso think if their s/o refuses to use her quirk bc she's like credence, an obscurus, and she...
question: Can i ask what would Iida and shinso think if their s/o refuses to use her quirk bc she's like credence, an obscurus, and she fears to lose control? I dremt about this tonight and it was sad yet awesome Thanks for your time❤️
answer:
Thank you for sending a request❤️


It took me a moment to realize that you meant Credence from fantastic beasts!


I’m not super into the fandom so I hope this still turned out how you wanted it even though it’s short.


Iida

  • Iida understands that you don’t want to use it and shares your worries because of how unpredictable it can be.
  • When it manifests accidentally he is quick to calm you and it down. Afterwards when you fall into his arms, crying, he kisses your forehead and reassures you that it is going to be alright.

Shinso

  • He understands how you feel, seeing that his quirk was always seen as one of a villain.
  • He would encourage you try to learn how to control it and help you with it as much as possible.
  • Would also comfort you and whenever you need it.

Mina: Well, it turns out he was gay.
